<stack-static>
    <statement><p><p>Differentiate <m>{\sin \left( 2\cdot x \right)}</m> with respect to <m>x</m>.</p><p/><ol marker="(1)">
<li><m>2\cdot \cos \left( 2\cdot x \right)</m></li>
<li><m>\sin \left( 2\cdot x \right)</m></li>
<li><m>-\frac{\cos \left( 2\cdot x \right)}{2}</m></li>
<li><m>\cos \left( 2\cdot x \right)+c</m></li>
<li>None of these</li>
</ol><div/></p></statement>
    <answer><p><m>(1)</m></p></answer>
